PROCESSING INFORMATION
----------------------
Standard processing time is 3-5 business days. Funds will be sent via your preferred method on file.

For wire transfers: Same-day processing available for requests received before 12:00 PM ET

For ACH transfers: 2-3 business days

For checks: 5-7 business days (includes mailing time)

IMPORTANT TAX INFORMATION
-------------------------
* Distributions from retirement accounts may be subject to federal and state income tax
* Early withdrawals (before age 59½) may incur a 10% penalty
* Required Minimum Distributions (RMDs) must be taken by December 31st
* A 1099-R will be issued for tax reporting purposes

